---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy" description="What Qazaq Lens collects, what it avoids collecting and how correction reports are stored.">
  <article class="wrap article-shell"><p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p><h1>Minimal data by design.</h1><div class="article-body">
    <h2>Normal reading</h2><p>The site does not use advertising trackers, fingerprinting, user accounts or behavioural profiles. Cloudflare may process technical request data required to deliver and protect the site.</p>
    <h2>Privacy-friendly analytics</h2><p>If Web Analytics is enabled, Qazaq Lens uses Cloudflare Web Analytics for aggregated page performance and visit statistics. It is not used to create advertising profiles or identify individual readers. The analytics module is disabled until its Cloudflare token is explicitly configured by the site maintainer.</p>
    <h2>Comments and correction reports</h2><p>Comments may store a name, optional email, page slug, comment text, timestamp and moderation status. Email is not published. Correction reports may store the page URL, issue, reasoning, supporting source, optional suggested wording, optional name and optional email. Pending comments and reports are visible only to the project moderator. Do not submit sensitive personal information.</p><p>Suggested myths and selected-text context use a mail draft addressed to <a href="mailto:nazkari86@gmail.com">nazkari86@gmail.com</a>; Gmail may process that message separately from Cloudflare. Sending it is your choice.</p>
    <p>To limit automated abuse, submission requests use a one-way SHA-256 hash of the network IP for a short-lived hourly rate-limit bucket. Raw IP addresses are not stored, and rate-limit buckets older than 48 hours are deleted automatically.</p>
    <h2>Local preferences</h2><p>Your theme choice and offline cache are stored on your own device. They are not sent to Qazaq Lens.</p>
    <h2>Retention and deletion</h2><p>Comments and correction reports are retained only as long as needed for moderation, editorial review and the public correction history. Public histories omit private contact details. To request deletion of a comment, report or email address, contact the editor with the page and approximate submission date.</p>
    <h2>Minors and sensitive information</h2><p>This site is not designed to collect information from children. Do not submit identifying, health, political-safety or other sensitive personal information through comments, corrections or email drafts.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2><p>Use the <a href="/report-error">correction form</a> for content and privacy concerns.</p>
  </div></article>
</BaseLayout>
